channel.title: Code snippets here!
channel.description:
Tired of seeing a bunch of topics that support 5-10 lines of code and are just backed up by flame or nothing. I thought it would be a good to have this thread to keep things nice and organized. Table of contents will be organized in 3 sections-5 sections for the different sources. Whatever you post here, please have it be [b]your work[/b]. It does not matter what it is, as long as it relates to the rsc server/client. Also please keep in mind to use the [InsertCode] feature and properly indent. Ok thanks. Lets kick this off.
Table of Contents [Source] + [Name] + [Author] organized by the source.
